title: King's College London - Strand Campus Tour (Monday, Tuesday and Thursday)
desc: We would like to invite you to take a guided group tour of our?Strand Campus, which will give you the opportunity to have a look around our campus a nd speak to a current King's student. 14:30-15:00: Welcome to King's College London and Question and Answer session 15:00-15:45: Guided Campus Tour If you would like to go on a Strand campus tour on a Wednesday or Friday, which will also include the chance to visit the Waterloo campus (for students interested in studying business management) or the Maughan Library (for all students), please go to? https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/kings-college-london-strand-campus-tour-wednesdays-and-fridays-tickets-17878073800 Important booking information:
